Dear ${userName},

We noticed an attempted setup of Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) on your account at ${dateNow}.

If you initiated this action, you can disregard this notification.

However, if you did not attempt to set up MFA, please secure your account immediately and contact our support team at support@goavanto.com for further assis...

Dear ${userName},

We're pleased to inform you that Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) has been successfully set up on your account.

This additional security measure will help protect your account from unauthorized access and enhance data security.

If you have any questions or concerns regarding MFA or your account security, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at
